        "created_at": "2016-10-22T03:25:57.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p><a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com/note.asp?iWine=2216389&amp;iNote=5959337\"><strong>2014 Francois Carillon Saint-Aubin 1er Cru Les Murgers des Dents de Chien</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Beaune, Saint-Aubin 1er Cru (10/21/2016)</em><br>\nLight hay in color, there is nice medium intensity to start, but misses some acidity, and shows a distinct sweep/ripe note on the finish. Overall just a bit fat and riper than I prefer, missing the zing I\u2019d like to see from St Aubin. <em><strong>(89 pts.)</strong></em></p>",
